"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?39/0/39946?source=related_link\">",
"      Overview of the management of sickle cell disease",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?35/11/36025?source=related_link\">",
"      Pathophysiology of alpha thalassemia",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?7/55/8058?source=related_link\">",
"      Pathophysiology of beta thalassemia",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
